                    Fast, decisive action when security incidents occur. Our expert team is available 24/7 to contain, eradicate, and recover from cyber threats.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt mr-2"></i> Emergency Hotline
