                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Containment</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Immediate actions to limit the impact and prevent further damage.</p>
